wideawake
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a soft felt hat with a broad brim and a low flat crown, the common headgear of early settlers and pioneers(cf BUSH-HAT)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
